 The National Youth Council Council of Nigeria, NYCN, has said that the governor of Zamfara State, Dr. Bello Matawallen possesses the strategies to end insecurity in the state, saying he should be supported to restore security in the state. June 17, 2019 In "News" The insecurity in the north yesterday triggered massive protest in Katsina metropolis, as thousands of youths took to the streets against what they described as incessant killings in seven frontline local government areas of the state by bandits. June 17, 2020 In "News" The Ministry of Defence has warned traditional rulers, highly placed politicians and other sponsors of armed banditry in the North West fanning the killings and other insecurity in the area to retrace their steps as security agencies are now out to visit the full wrath of the law on them. April 9, 2019 In "News"